  "description": "<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Upravo kao što je slučaj sa ugrađenim citatom, možete dodati i atribut <code>cite</code> na blok citat.</p>\n<p>Evo primera bloka cita sa atributom <code>cite</code>:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-html\">&#x3C;blockquote cite=\"https://www.freecodecamp.org/news/is-college-worth-it/\">\n  The first thing you should consider about education is this is an economic decision.\n&#x3C;/blockquote>\n</code></pre>\n<p>Sada dodajte atribut <code>cite</code> na blok citat sa URL-om <code>https://www.freecodecamp.org/news/learn-to-code-book/</code>.</p>\n</section>",
